sentence: Why did the cookie get fired from his job? he came to work baked.
explanation: The term baked can mean being under the influence of drugs (especially marijuana) and also refer to food that has been cooked in an oven.
first_new_sentence: The chefs baked the cookies until they were golden brown.
second_new_sentence: He was so baked that he couldnt remember where he parked his car.
